# How to use
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Create a script and name it Whatever you wish
2. Place the script in ServerScriptService
3. Create team colors, the script uses colors from the color section below, but you can change them with no adverse effects
4. Tag your parts with the same color that you have defined as the variable such as "BlackZone".


---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#Colors Used In Original Script
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
local TEAM_ZONE_TAGS = {
	["BlackZone"] = "Really black",
	["BlueZone"] = "Electric blue",
	["GreenZone"] = "Lime green",
	["OrangeZone"] = "Deep orange",
	["PinkZone"] = "Hot pink",
	["PurpleZone"] = "Magenta",
	["RedZone"] = "Really red",
	["YellowZone"] = "New Yeller",
}
